Selenium WebDriver
--------------
Alerts/popups
-----
driver.switchTo().alert()

dismiss()
accept()
sendKeys()
getText()



Authencated popup
------
driver.get("http://the-internet.herokuapp.com/basic_auth");

Syntax:
http://username:password@url.com

http://admin:admin@the-internet.herokuapp.com/basic_auth


iframes/Frames
------------------

driver.switchTo().frame("Name of the frame");
driver.switchTo().frame("ID of the frame");
driver.switchTo().frame(driver.findElement(By.xpath("//frame"));
driver.switchTo().frame(index)

Handle Browser windows
----------------------

driver.getWindowHandle() --> returns the window ID of current window
driver.getWindowHandles() --> returns teh window ID's of multiple browser windows

driver.switchTo().window(windowID)


Single ---> close()
Multiple browsers --->quit()